---
title: Dukkah-Crusted Cauliflower & Spiced Kumara Salad with Mint Yoghurt & Currants
description: This delightful dish is a celebration of wholesome roasted veggies with chermoula-spiced kumara and fragrant mint. Add dukkah to roasted cauliflower for extra flavour and crunch, then top it off with a scattering of sweet currants.
